      "note": "summary",
      "abstract": "Permits the Department of Human Services to place an Indian child in an out-of-state placement without requiring the placement to be licensed by or under contract with the department or to be a qualified residential treatment facility if certain standards are met. Declares an emergency, effective on passage."
